data.title: A Part of You Soundtrack (2024). Music List From the Movie
data.meta_description: A Part of You Soundtrack 2024 (En del av dig): Here is a complete list of music. The entire list of songs from the Swedish Netflix movie
data.text:
A Part of You Soundtrack (2024). A Swedish Netflix film directed by Sigge Eklund and written by Michaela Hamilton. Music from the movie bellow.

Life and death that portrays the experience of being 17 years old and feeling like your heart is about to burst from your chest. Agnes’ older sister Julia possesses everything that Agnes dreams of: she’s the coolest person in school, the center of every party, and she’s dating Noel.

If only Agnes could be more like her. When the worst possible thing occurs, Agnes’ world is turned upside down and she’s forced to reinvent herself. Suddenly, she’s on the verge of obtaining everything she’s ever desired, but at what cost?

Cast: Felicia Maxime as Agnes, Edvin Ryding as Noel, Zara Larsson as Julia, Ida Engvoll, Mustafa Al-Mashhadani, Alva Bratt, Emil Hedayat, Olivia Essén, Nikki Hanselblad, Maxwell Cunningham

Genres: Drama

Release Date: May 31, 2024

Original Title: En del av dig
